I'm scared to death in the house of Freddy! The Joy of Creation: Reborn is a Free Roam Five Nights at Freddy's clone, and it is terrifying. The jumpscares may be super intense, but the Easter eggs are super cool. I hope Nikson continues to make this game into its full version.
